        <h1>Dissemination of Erasmus+ Project Results — Seminar for Teachers from Vratsa Region</h1>
        <p class="lead-meta">PPMG "Acad. Ivan Tsenov" · July 7, 2025 · 11:00 · Education · Sponsored</p>
